# Patch My PC's full SCUP/WSUS catalog export (~16 MB) used as the source
# for Util/build-patchmypc-catalog.ps1 — too large/churny to track in git.
# Re-export it from Patch My PC and place it at Util/PatchMyPC.xml before
# running the build script; only the derived patchmypc-catalog.json is
# committed.
Util/PatchMyPC.xml

# Patch My PC's official supported-products feed (~6 MB), the source of
# truth for which apps are supported and how to detect them. Downloaded
# automatically by build-patchmypc-catalog.ps1 (or pass -SkipDownload to
# reuse an existing local copy) — too large to track in git.
Util/supportedproducts.xml
